/strong> felt Daily Nourishing Shampoo was gentle yet effective in cleansing hair.* <\/li><li><strong>92%<\/strong> felt their\/their child's hair looked shiny and healthy after using Daily Nourishing Shampoo.* <\/li><li><strong>96%<\/strong> felt their\/their child's scalp felt clean and replenished after using Daily Nourishing Shampoo.*<\/li><\/ul>","page":""}},"147e9960-c5fe-44f4-8469-9583a9752a0a":{"type":"review","disabled":true,"settings":{"title_tab":"Reviews"}},"2e69c5c0-ab83-4cda-9c38-1aaab6fdf1cc":{"type":"related-product","settings":{"title_heading":"Buy with","size_text":"h6","product_limit":3}}},"block_order":["6889c9ba-caef-4edd-9757-6711505cb095","b69a53cf-5bc1-4b18-add3-92af436f966c","450a0011-a13e-4bad-9fbb-454bc0a862b4","f4c1b859-6506-4354-b686-25d6efffda01","147e9960-c5fe-44f4-8469-9583a9752a0a","2e69c5c0-ab83-4cda-9c38-1aaab6fdf1cc"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"animation":"fade-up","setwidth":"container","tab_size":"large","enable_left":true,"paddingsection":"48px 0px 20px 0px","paddingmobile":"32px 0px 32px 0px","marginsection":"0px 0px 0px 0px","marginmobile":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}},"be561305-5bee-4018-a668-c8770086ba5b":{"type":"line","settings":{"animation":"","paddingsection":"0px 0px 0px 0px","marginsection":"0px 0px 0px 0px","bgsection":"#ffffff","setwidth":"container","bgborder":"#dddddd","wborder":"1px"}},"c5690cdb-c04d-45fd-9c6c-cfee011363ca":{"type":"service","blocks":{"template--14684877652053__c5690cdb-c04d-45fd-9c6c-cfee011363ca-166585292003960893-0":{"type":"service","settings":{"bgblock":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","title":"Free Shipping","description":"From all orders over $100","icon":"<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\" class=\"icon icon-truck\" viewbox=\"0 0 82 82\"><path d=\"M7.238 68.717H1.867V2.12H58.4v16.736h3.886c9.755 0 17.663 7.908 17.663 17.663v32.199h-5.917M55.781 68.717H25.487\"><\/path><path d=\"M58.334 42.124h15.068v-4.27c0-6.82-5.53-12.35-12.351-12.35h-2.718v16.62M73.909 70.236a9.125 9.125 0 1 0-1